# TempoSimple's Cheat Sheet

## Aliases

    alias ts='php app/console'

## Punch new time card

    ts punch task end-hour
    ts punch task end-hour -S start-hour -D description -p project -d day

## Reports

    ts daily
    ts daily -d day

    ts weekly

    ts billable
    ts billable -p project -m month

## Options, default values and time formats

    -d --day         {{ today.getDay }} Format: `Y-m-d` (e.g. `1989-01-25`)
    -D --description
    -m --month       {{ today.getMonth }}    Format: `Y-m` (e.g. `2004-09`)
    -p --project     {{ defaultProject }}
    -S --start-hour  {{ startHour }}      Format: `H:i` (e.g. `09:00`, `13:45`)
